News related to RSE Asia Association




Featured news
A news item published by Australian Research Data Commons highlights RSE Asia among other work presented during the “Vive la differénce” workshop organized by the Research Software Alliance (13 May 2022).
The Open Life Science (OLS) team planted a tree dedicated to its cohort-4 in the OLS forest. RSE Asia was launched as a project in the cohort-4 of the OLS programme (11 May 2022).
RSE Asia got featured in the Collaborations Workshop 2022 highlights blogpost by the Software Sustainability Institute (28 April 2022).
















